Package com.stuypulse.stuylib.util

Class StopWatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stuypulse.stuylib.util.StopWatch
  • public class StopWatch
extends java.lang.Object
    This StopWatch class helps classes who want their functions to be time independant do that by giving them an easy way to get intervals of time. This is better than just doing it in the class because it stores the time as a long to keep accuracy, but converts it into a double for convenience.
